        <Parent_String>factory centers [300387303], industrial centers (inhabited places) [300387302], settlements by economic base [300120583], inhabited places [300008347], Settlements and Landscapes (hierarchy name) [300008346], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
